AWS Command Line

#aws s3 ls
 - lists all buckets globally

enter # aws configure
enter AWS Access Key ID:
enter AWS Secret Access Key:
Default region name: eu-west-2 (or wherever)

aws credentials live in .aws/ directory

#aws ec2 describe -instances
	-describes all instances both running and terminated

#aws ec2 terminate-instances --instance-ids <instancename>

user access keys are less secure
